spanGrp.span: We celebrate the Virgin Mary’s day on the twenty eighth of August.
We celebrate the Virgin Mary’s day from the early morning.
In my family we wake up early and to go to the church, everybody is already there, we light our candles and we walk around with the sacrifice and slaughter it.
bänım semyam diah ki ğalhirıh gidirıh halhta orda äp eğılirıh ğurbani kimın var götürirıh mumumuzi yahirıh ğurbanımızi fırladirıh käsirıh
